# 🤖 AI Resume Screening System

An AI-based system that analyzes resumes and matches them with job descriptions using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 📄 Upload resumes (PDF, DOCX, TXT)
* 🧠 Extract and clean text data
* 🎯 Match resumes with job description
* 📊 Rank candidates based on similarity score
* 🛠 Extract important skills automatically

---

## 🧠 Technologies Used

* Python
* Scikit-learn (TF-IDF, Cosine Similarity)
* NLTK (Text Processing)
* PyPDF2 (PDF parsing)
* python-docx (DOCX parsing)

